槍，絕不兒戲！我地30幾歲既前線好明顯呢樣野，我地係拎條命同全家既將來去陪你地去抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n但理大前線同學仔，你地有d係度 男男女女飲啤酒吹水，飲左酒好打d? 有點哨兵仲係度轉水樽玩真心話....我地係無言至極，咁樣真係值得我地冒險咩？我想問 遲點係咪會有打邊爐？唱k 跳舞，表演乒乓波？我地係打緊仗阿！！可唔可以認真d阿！可唔可以收起玩樂幼稚既行為阿！你話得放鬆下打下波 練下體能 都好阿！<br />\n你係度玩Truth or Dare ？你係咪吊得小阿！<br />\n所以點解咁多人非常失望離開！！<br />\n捉鬼未捉到未確實又惡言相向，好似個個都係嫌疑犯咁！"},{"pid":"f05618afcc6ab171ba06e074f7763bdd06f017a5","tid":1727050,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9061cbf2ba316cdeaac3a9a7457ef15acee66120","tid":1727050,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:45:35.000Z","msg":"手足小心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1</a><br />\n深度分析，大家可以都睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb9bce3233275ad4cc155177249a866c8f9e7ba","tid":1727050,"uid":8850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"要人啊"},{"pid":"7aa5314a250caadc94aebbd40bdd0014ac3a9d6a","tid":1727050,"uid":301884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbaaccef82842a13410629deaa877c308fb3ed03","tid":1727050,"uid":303913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:38:16.000Z","msg":"防暴落地！"},{"pid":"2b4322558cbf92669b088bf28f3ea977bdd1fcfb","tid":1727050,"uid":8850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"要人啊啊啊啊"},{"pid":"ddd591cffebe0b6303309ce6083784464f3b19fb","tid":1727050,"uid":303913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0126ad6e82b37fd24d58d4e856e08e342c55e959","tid":1727050,"uid":277816,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:20:00.000Z","msg":